fields.title: MSI GF63 Thin Core i5 10th Gen Laptop
fields.description:
This laptop is a hot pick for those whose budget is around 65k and who want to experience the RTX 3050 GPU. The only con of this laptop is its Generation, as it comes with 10th gen, but wait guys, lemme tell you the truth. If your budget is tight and you really want a great laptop, then you can go with it.

It has a 10th gen core i5 processor (6 cores and 12 threads). It has RTX 3050 GPU with 4GB VRAM. The display of this laptop is 15.6 inches with 144 Hz.

fields.title: ASUS TUF A15 (2021) Gaming, Business (AMD Ryzen 7 4800H) Laptop
fields.description:
This laptop is a true beast guys, it comes with an octa-core processor. Though the gen is 4th and not the latest one, still it defeats most of the 5th gen processors, if you want my simple answer then yes it is better than Ryzen 5 5600H processor. If these generations don’t matter to you, then you can buy this laptop without thinking twice.

It comes with Ryzen 7 4800H (8 cores and 16 threads) processor. And it has a 144Hz 15.6-inch display. It has an 8GB Ram pre-installed on it, but you can upgrade the RAM to 32 Gigabytes according to your needs. And it has RTX 3050 GPU with 4GB VRAM.
